{"tid":1892220,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我諗我哋必須𠄘認泛民一定會行溫和路線","createTime":"2020-02-22T11:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T11:44:43.000Z","uid":104767,"like":21,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0a71f37daa1dbcf877734170c506211ab2be2746","tid":1892220,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"其實泛民冇政治需要聽獨派/本土/深黃如朱凱迪嘅意見，中間派選民先係左右泛民議席嘅票源，佢哋唔敢得罪，唯有犧牲激進意見。<br />\n本土派雖然佔泛民15-20%票源，但係泛民毋須用實際抗爭行動取得其選票。喺本土派冇參選權嘅情況下，本土派票源會自動流入泛民，唔成功嘅話可以用道德綁架方式，如「投白票係熱狗、最緊要建制輸」之類取得選票，相反中間派選票必須用實際行動取得，否則會流入建制派。<br />\n你係泛民理性上會點揀？其實佢哋肯盡幫抗爭者，純粹出於善心，已經超出自己政治需要。"},{"pid":"b8962fd35dfae97c76a016e3d1713d7af3c10d27","tid":1892220,"uid":78304,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:34:42.000Z","msg":"溫水煮蛙 夠溫和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b430c2b64087811b408c4a88827b77309987721","tid":1892220,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe2a458aa31c277f889833d602c4b5724a6e306","tid":1892220,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"關於黃色經濟圈 我有兩個大膽嘅想法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1892285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1892285</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f095b41878de9f4812beb4d9a4b8bc43c8196521","tid":1892220,"uid":104767,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"我認自己之前高估本土派政治能量，妄想可以要求泛民本土化。<br />\n之前太串屌泛民唔好意思"},{"pid":"504c6537ebed75e7bcb5b9f42f1f732f7211832f","tid":1892220,"uid":104767,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b8962fd35dfae97c76a016e3d1713d7af3c10d27","tid":1892220,"uid":78304,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:34:42.000Z","msg":"溫水煮蛙 夠溫和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202